column5: I have been to the Bass Tournament on Rainy Lake and had a blast. Wondering if anyone knows of private cabin rentals in the area for the whole month of August.

I have a 3bedroom cabin on Rainy sleeps about 6-7 its on an island and has power ect.-very private over 5 acres-located just 15 min boat ride from US in Canadian waters -usually rents for500/week US but if you are interested in the whole month?-email [email protected] thanks WALLI
